{"TopicId":165153,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How to make Turret mounts and bearings?","CreatedByName":"Glitchgamer12","CreatedById":181093,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-04T10:35:03Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Glitchgamer12","CreatedById":181093,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-04T10:35:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo i need some advice on how to make turret mounts and bearings, currently i am using a hollow liquid fuel tube and a separator at the bottom and then putting octagon struts in to make a \u0022hinge\u0022 kinda thing. But when i load my craft it sadly tilts horribly, so i tightened it and it just glitched out \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\u00A0 Any help would be great!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ThreePounds","CreatedById":116058,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-04T11:45:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWithout pictures it\u0027s hard to know what you\u0027re doing wrong. Maybe post some screenshots?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFrom my limited experience with such contraptions it\u0027s vital that the two parts that are moving relative to each other are actually separate craft. You can either achieve this with a separator or a set of docking ports for a resettable connection. The trick is to keep the two parts from falling out of alignment before you separate them though as the colliers won\u0027t be respected. But without screen shots that\u0027s as much as I can help you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-04T13:29:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, as advice, use \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E balls in hinges. They are super smooth, especially when multiple are clipped together.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Glitchgamer12","CreatedById":181093,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-04T14:20:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do you mean by \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E balls? You mean the place anywhere linear \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E ports?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: I\u0027ll get some pics tommarow,, right now it\u0027s 10:21 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-09-04T14:21:55Z\u0022 title=\u002209/04/2017 02:21  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 4, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Glitchgamer12\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-05T03:50:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223164702\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022165153\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221504534803\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181093\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Glitchgamer12\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, Glitchgamer12 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do you mean by \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E balls? You mean the place anywhere linear \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E ports?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes exactly those. People including my self have used them to great effect in things like these.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/tz8A97t.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022tz8A97t.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe rotor assembly is held on by \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E balls. Literally nothing else.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Glitchgamer12","CreatedById":181093,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-05T05:39:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223165276\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022165153\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221504583459\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160994\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022qzgy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, qzgy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022tz8A97t.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/tz8A97t.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow that\u0027s an interesting design! When I get back I\u0027ll try that out. Also how would you arrange them? Can I get a close up view of the bearings?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-06T00:36:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223165318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022165153\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221504589970\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181093\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Glitchgamer12\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, Glitchgamer12 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso how would you arrange them? Can I get a close up view of the bearings?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey are arranged so that a group of \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E balls is holding one in the middle, attached to the moving part (in this case, some mechanical contraption) Two sets are used so that it is firmly sandwiched to make sure the parts don\u0027t move.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/xipjAiC.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022xipjAiC.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve built a turret kinda thing, take a look at how it works. Uses the same \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E ball technique. Helps I think the most to actually take a look.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/7bk7rifl7ek6dui/turret.craft?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/7bk7rifl7ek6dui/turret.craft?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Glitchgamer12","CreatedById":181093,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-06T01:50:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor some reason I still don\u0027t get that\u00A0picture \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-06T23:49:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223166005\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022165153\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221504662612\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181093\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Glitchgamer12\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 hours ago, Glitchgamer12 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor some reason I still don\u0027t get that\u00A0picture \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk huh.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022xipjAiC.png?1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/xipjAiC.png?1\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe thing in green rotates. The ball in blue is attached to the thing in green. The red balls holds it stationary, but allows it to rotate since its not the same craft. Understand more?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, might be a good idea to check out the craft\u00A0 file. Might make more sense than from pictures.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Glitchgamer12","CreatedById":181093,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-07T01:29:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDropbox is banned in China \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso I\u0027m absent from my computer for a few months, but this info is very useful for other people \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}